  <name>PostMock</name>
  <summary>Modern API testing tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      PostMock is a modern, cross-platform API testing tool built with Tauri and Vue 3.
      It provides a clean and intuitive interface for testing HTTP APIs with powerful features
      for developers and QA engineers.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>HTTP request testing - Support for GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH, HEAD, OPTIONS methods</li>
      <li>Collection and folder management - Organize your API requests efficiently</li>
      <li>Environment variables - Manage multiple environments with variable substitution</li>
      <li>Request history - Automatic tracking of all request history</li>
      <li>Automated testing - Built-in test assertions and global variable extraction</li>
      <li>Dark mode support - Switch between light and dark themes</li>
      <li>Data persistence - Local file system storage for your data</li>
      <li>Import/Export - Share collections with your team</li>
      <li>cURL import - Quickly create requests from cURL commands</li>
      <li>Code editor - Syntax highlighting for JSON, XML, and HTML</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      PostMock is designed to be lightweight, fast, and easy to use, making it perfect for
      API development, testing, and debugging workflows.
    </p>
  </description>
  
